Package org.treetank.saxon.wrapper Description

Treetank wrappers.

The wrappers implement the core interfaces of Saxon. Treetank's node type implementations are wrapped into Saxon's internal representation of nodes.

Author:
Johannes Lichtenberger, University of Konstanz
